24:12.584 --> 24:15.586
Sleep is coming.

24:17.656 --> 24:20.224
Sleep.

24:25.964 --> 24:28.266
- Did it work?
- Appears so.

24:28.267 --> 24:30.234
Very good.

24:31.770 --> 24:33.505
What do you think?

24:33.506 --> 24:35.773
You're Merlin the wizard.

24:35.774 --> 24:37.642
