24:37.643 --> 24:40.010
Neither can I.

24:40.112 --> 24:44.081
Seems to reach a part of the
brain that isn't physical.

24:44.149 --> 24:46.550
If one could suggest to
someone who was hypnotized

24:46.585 --> 24:49.453
to do all sorts of humorous feats,

24:49.521 --> 24:52.122
then why not use it for
something more practical?

24:52.123 --> 24:54.825
Change people's perception.

24:54.826 --> 24:56.293
Curb their addiction.

24:56.294 --> 24:58.328
I've heard crazier ideas.

24:58.329 --> 25:00.630
In this room, actually.

25:00.632 --> 25:03.467
What habits does your subject have?

25:07.838 --> 25:10.139
Simple, direct instructions.

25:18.349 --> 25:21.885
- Mr. Cleary...
- Mm.

25:21.886 --> 25:23.387
...when I blow on you,

25:23.388 --> 25:26.390
you will wake and you will no longer

25:26.391 --> 25:28.492
be interested in smoking your pipe.

25:30.562 --> 25:32.662
You will detest it.

25:34.499 --> 25:36.766
The sight of it will anger you.

25:46.577 --> 25:48.511
The fuck is that?

25:48.512 --> 25:50.479
- It's your pipe.
- No. No.

25:50.481 --> 25:52.015
- That ain't mine.
- Yes, it is.

25:52.016 --> 25:54.150
- No.
- Do you want it?

25:54.151 --> 25:57.653
You bet your ass I do.

25:57.687 --> 26:00.222
I'm sorry, Doc, but
all that hocus-pocus...

26:00.323 --> 26:03.358
Yeah, thanks for wasting
our time. Go on, get out.

26:05.428 --> 26:09.564
