paper about your mother.

27:12.094 --> 27:14.028
I'm sorry.

27:16.231 --> 27:18.733
I need the speed of this place.

27:18.734 --> 27:20.801
Of you.

27:22.104 --> 27:24.805
Maybe I've changed.

27:24.907 --> 27:28.442
Perhaps I'm not as reckless
and fast as you remember.

27:30.278 --> 27:33.814
Algernon told me that last month you
performed surgery with a telephone.

27:36.517 --> 27:40.120
Some things have changed, I promise you.

27:40.188 --> 27:43.223
They have with me, too,
or else I wouldn't be here.

27:44.458 --> 27:46.759
I know now that this is where I belong.

27:48.996 --> 27:51.164
I've always known that.

27:59.974 --> 28:02.142
What's he saying?

28:02.143 --> 28:03.943
He doesn't like you being here.

28:04.045 --> 28:07.613
I'm just trying to help him
and get some information.

28:07.615 --> 28:10.015
How long has he been like this?

28:19.126 --> 28:21.894
Has he seen anyone from
the health department?

28:28.668 --> 28:30.069
He's afraid you're trying to deport him.

28:30.070 --> 28:31.403
Assure him I'm not.

28:34.875 --> 28:39.543
He's saying that the guy from the
health department threatened to.

28:39.544 --> 28:41.846
Was his name Speight?

28:41.847 --> 28:43.648
Do you know? Speight?

28:48.220 --> 28:49.888
He's saying he was a pig.

28:49.889 --> 28:51.422
Fat like a barrel.

28:51.423 --> 28:53.624
Speight.

28:53.659 --> 28:57.561
Did you give this to Inspector Speight?

29:09.408 --> 29:11.275
