feeling not well and in a week he died.

29:41.539 --> 29:43.406
Did your brother have money?

29:43.407 --> 29:45.241
Was he well-off?

29:47.477 --> 29:48.636
No.

29:48.662 --> 29:52.115
Then how could he afford
a second-class ticket?

30:04.794 --> 30:06.329
He doesn't know.

30:06.330 --> 30:08.297
He doesn't know, but look,

30:08.298 --> 30:10.399
maybe Aldo stole it.

30:10.433 --> 30:12.934
But Gino came here
honestly. He's a good man.

30:13.003 --> 30:15.671
He has a family, a job, you
know? He didn't do no wrong.

30:20.510 --> 30:22.210
You must leave, I'm sorry.

30:22.345 --> 30:25.013
- He needs to see a doctor.
- He wants you to leave. I'm sorry.

30:25.014 --> 30:27.249
Of course. I'm sorry.

30:45.334 --> 30:48.436
After the swelling goes down, try to...

30:48.470 --> 30:50.438
keep it elevated and then you can go home.

30:50.439 --> 30:51.972
Excuse me one moment.

30:56.712 --> 30:58.680
Lucy.

31:01.017 --> 31:04.219
I'm sorry. I'm sure that
must have been a surprise.

31:04.220 --> 31:06.021
A pleasant one.

31:06.022 --> 31:07.655
Welcome back.

31:09.190 --> 31:11.758
I know I felt more than you at one point,

31:11.826 --> 31:13.560
but I won't pretend my
treatment towards you

31:13.628 --> 31:15.996
after our falling out
wasn't intended to hurt you.

31:15.997 --> 31:17.531
It did.

31:17.532 --> 31:19.999
Well, I was angry.

31:21.069 --> 31:23.637
And I acted like a child.

31:23.638 --> 31:25.672
And I'm sorry.

31:27.242 --> 31:29.876
I didn't expect you to forgive me.

31:29.877 --> 31:31.810
Well, I have.

31:31.812 --> 31:33.746
I've learned a lot about forgiveness.

31:33.847 --> 31:36.816
And though I don't expect it,
I hope you'll give me yours.

31:36.817 --> 31:38.984
Of course.

31:40.187 --> 31:42.755
I'd give anything to be friends again.

31:42.756 --> 31:44.557
Me, too.

31:45.993 --> 31:48.161
There's a ball coming up.

31:48.162 --> 31:49.995
Excuse me?

31:50.030 --> 31:53.466
To raise money for the new hospital.

31:53.500 --> 31:55.901
I heard you have a new lady friend.

31:55.902 --> 31:57.903
Oh.

31:57.938 --> 31:59.704
I just thought that if
you wanted to attend,

31:59.706 --> 32:01.907
it would only be fair to her...

32:01.908 --> 32:03.776
I don't know her name.

32:03.777 --> 32:06.078
Genevieve.

32:06.112 --> 32:08.513
To give her ample warning
so that she has time

32:08.515 --> 32:10.482
to get a dress and prepare.

32:11.250 --> 32:13.251
Thank you.

32:13.252 --> 32:15.053
Are you going?

32:15.054 --> 32:17.722
We'll see.

32:23.763 --> 32:25.863
Algie's gonna have Thackery ask the board

32:26.032 --> 32:30.602
if he can perform a surgery on
that D.W. Garrison Carr fellow.

32:32.138 --> 32:34.906
That Carr's in our boy's ear.

32:34.940 --> 32:38.677
Algie's got my vote,
but he's pushing harder

32:38.711 --> 32:41.546
than the rest of the board can stand.

32:41.547 --> 32:44.449
Carr does more harm than good.

32:44.450 --> 32:47.486
Good afternoon.

32:47.487 --> 32:48.920
Let me have a Glenlivit.

32:48.921 --> 32:50.721
- Two, please.
- Yes, sir.

32:50.722 --> 32:52.589
It's too soon.

32:54.393 --> 32:56.627
Barrow said he's received
inquiries from nervous donors

32:56.661 --> 32:59.095
about Algie's involvement going forward.

32:59.097 --> 33:01.264
It's just one surgery.

33:01.299 --> 33:03.967
And Algie invented it, for God's sake.

33:04.002 --> 33:06.837
I'm not quibbling about our boy's skill.

33:06.905 --> 33:09.306
I would take him over Thackery these days.

33:09.307 --> 33:11.875
But our donors believe Thack is a god

33:11.943 --> 33:14.477
and we need them to
continue believing that.

33:20.818 --> 33:22.618
It's not just...

33:22.620 --> 33:24.788
it's not just their estimation

33:24.789 --> 33:27.190
of Thackery that matters.

33:27.258 --> 33:30.760
They clearly don't want
the new Knick integrated.

33:30.862 --> 33:33.664
Meaning having a Negro
doctor or his Negro patients?

33:33.665 --> 33:35.332
Both.

33:35.366 --> 33:38.701
If we want Algie to move uptown with us,

33:38.702 --> 33:41.871
we have to sacrifice something.

33:43.807 --> 33:45.607
So the patients.

34:01.357 --> 34:04.025
So the barge takes all
the lower-class passengers

34:04.060 --> 34:06.327
over to Ellis Island
for the full inspection,

34:06.362 --> 34:08.862
but a doc gives them
a quick once-over here.

34:08.864 --> 34:11.199
What happens if they get marked?

34:11.301 --> 34:13.469
Well, then they got to
see another doctor on Ellis

34:13.469 --> 34:14.936
for a more thorough exam.

34:14.971 --> 34:16.670
If the doc thinks they're too sick

34:16.672 --> 34:18.005
and can't get cured easy here,

34:18.039 --> 34:19.540
then they can't come into the country.

34:19.541 --> 34:21.875
Over 25,000 last year alone.

34:21.876 --> 34:24.143
Where did they all go?

34:24.146 --> 34:26.679
Back to where they came from.

34:26.681 --> 34:28.716
What would send them back?

34:28.717 --> 34:31.185
Anything highly contagious.

34:31.186 --> 34:33.588
Trachoma, typhus, cholera...

34:33.589 --> 34:35.489
- Plague?
- Oh, yeah.

34:35.591 --> 34:38.558
And they'd have to go back
to their country of origin?

34:38.559 --> 34:40.226
Not with embarkation.

34:40.328 --> 34:42.562
See, the shipping companies
have to pay a $100 fine

34:42.563 --> 34:44.330
for each and passage back,

34:44.431 --> 34:48.266
so most of the big companies
do their own health inspections

34:48.335 --> 34:50.837
before the immigrants even
leave their home ports.

34:50.904 --> 34:53.873
The thing is, over there,
people always get through.

34:53.873 --> 34:55.974
We don't miss them on this end.

34:57.710 --> 35:00.045
Is it this crowded every day?

35:00.046 --> 35:02.347
Yeah, and it's getting worse, too.

35:02.449 --> 35:05.617
And this is just the third-class
and the steerage passengers.

35:05.685 --> 35:08.287
What about the first and
second-class passengers?

35:08.288 --> 35:10.221
They got off down there.

35:10.290 --> 35:12.257
Immigration officials
have already met the boats

35:12.359 --> 35:14.259
in the harbor and checked
them out right on the ship.

35:14.393 --> 35:16.694
There's very little risk of
something really infectious

35:16.795 --> 35:19.196
coming from the ones that
can pay to ride in comfort.

35:23.536 --> 35:25.470
Dr. Thackery.

35:25.471 --> 35:29.106
Someone, or maybe someones,

35:29.107 --> 35:30.875
