35:30.876 --> 35:33.010
They're waiting in your office.

35:35.113 --> 35:36.713
Excuse me.

35:44.422 --> 35:46.255
Mr. Brockhurst.

35:46.257 --> 35:48.391
Cab ride here was a dollar.

35:53.598 --> 35:56.300
The one on their right is Zoya
and the one on the left is Nika.

35:56.301 --> 35:58.402
- Say hello, girls.
- Hello.

35:58.403 --> 36:00.469
- Nika.
- Hello.

36:00.470 --> 36:03.139
