what you want them for.

36:21.325 --> 36:23.626
No, that is not what I want them for.

36:23.627 --> 36:25.061
Many men do.

36:25.129 --> 36:27.730
Not a one ever said it
wasn't worth the money.

36:29.366 --> 36:32.067
If you want to wait in the
lobby, I'll be about an hour.

36:37.207 --> 36:40.208
If you'll just follow me.

36:40.210 --> 36:41.943
All the modern gadgets...

36:41.945 --> 36:44.446
electric toaster, gas stove.

36:44.480 --> 36:46.614
They're even installing a dumbwaiter

36:46.649 --> 36:48.550
all the way from the service entrance

36:48.551 --> 36:50.952
for ice and food deliveries.

36:50.987 --> 36:52.720
I could learn to cook for you, Hermie.

36:52.722 --> 36:55.690
Ah, we'll hire someone for that.

36:55.691 --> 36:58.159
Cook you anything you want.

36:58.160 --> 36:59.961
When can we move in?

36:59.962 --> 37:03.130
Mmm, about a month or so.

37:03.165 --> 37:05.533
Every project in New York is being slowed

37:05.534 --> 37:08.302
because of the demand for workers.

37:08.371 --> 37:11.740
I'll need the time to
gather the rest of the funds

37:11.741 --> 37:14.208
to pay for your freedom.

37:14.209 --> 37:16.511
I don't want you spending a minute longer

37:16.512 --> 37:18.879
than you need to at Ping Wu's.

37:20.915 --> 37:24.217
So, can you see us here?

37:24.218 --> 37:26.152
It's beautiful.

37:32.327 --> 37:35.929
It would have been nice
to be able to see the park.

37:35.997 --> 37:39.198
Well, those apartments
are a bit more expensive.

37:39.199 --> 37:41.300
Oh.

37:41.335 --> 37:44.737
It's just with all of my expenses,

37:44.738 --> 37:46.706
we still have to buy furniture.

37:46.707 --> 37:48.908
I understand, Hermie.

37:48.942 --> 37:51.978
You're doing the best you can, I suppose.

38:04.925 --> 38:08.127
Just imagine if we were higher up.

38:08.261 --> 38:11.363
What it would be like to look
out the window when we fuck.

38:13.133 --> 38:15.200
I'd bend over...

38:16.903 --> 38:19.104
