information in order to do it.

39:46.356 --> 39:50.058
More examinations. More about your past.

39:50.060 --> 39:52.994
Not the story he makes you tell.

39:52.995 --> 39:55.196
The truth.

39:58.401 --> 40:00.868
How did you come to meet Mr. Brockhurst?

40:02.638 --> 40:05.873
We were living in forest in Siberia.

40:05.874 --> 40:07.976
He was an explorer.

40:07.977 --> 40:11.146
You're not onstage.

40:11.147 --> 40:13.348
It's just us.

40:18.687 --> 40:20.855
Where are you from originally?

40:22.058 --> 40:25.226
We were both born in Minsk.

40:25.261 --> 40:28.529
