you were born in Minsk,

40:28.530 --> 40:29.897
that would be a miracle.

40:33.268 --> 40:35.402
Our father didn't want us

40:35.437 --> 40:38.606
and sold us to circus when we were babies.

40:38.607 --> 40:42.176
We went from one to the next.

40:42.177 --> 40:46.647
Prague, Bologna, Marseilles,

40:46.782 --> 40:50.985
then Blackpool where Mr.
Brockhurst bought and bring us here.

40:52.754 --> 40:54.721
How does he treat you?

40:55.958 --> 40:58.259
Better than some.

40:59.895 --> 41:01.929
Have you ever been to school?

41:01.930 --> 41:03.563
Can you read?

41:03.565 --> 41:05.800
I know some letters and numbers.

41:05.801 --> 41:07.701
How about you, Nika?

41:08.603 --> 41:10.770
Nika is shy.

41:10.771 --> 41:12.873
She's smart, though.

41:12.874 --> 41:14.541
More than me.

41:16.211 --> 41:19.245
What does Mr. Brockhurst
say about working for him?

41:22.283 --> 41:25.552
