42:15.702 --> 42:19.338
Watch us kiss each other.

42:20.473 --> 42:22.607
Touch each other.

42:23.810 --> 42:25.610
Be with them.

42:26.713 --> 42:28.513
Jesus.

42:30.216 --> 42:33.651
