to get what I wanted.

42:53.306 --> 42:55.207
- Did you?
- I did.

42:55.208 --> 42:56.641
But I need to see them again.

42:56.642 --> 42:57.975
Why?

42:57.977 --> 43:00.645
Because as I was telling them,

43:00.713 --> 43:03.482
I believe it might be
possible to separate them.

43:03.483 --> 43:05.450
What, split them apart?

43:05.485 --> 43:07.519
For good? Why the fuck would I want that?

43:07.653 --> 43:10.522
No one's gonna pay to see two
girls who used to be connected.

43:10.556 --> 43:13.424
No, but they'd be able
to live a normal life.

43:13.425 --> 43:14.858
I don't give a good goddamn.

43:14.860 --> 43:16.394
Them girls make me money that way.

43:16.495 --> 43:18.455
Lots of it. And you're
not gonna monkey with that.

43:18.497 --> 43:20.431
I think they should decide for themselves.

43:20.565 --> 43:22.633
Who the fuck do you think you're
dealing with? They're mine.

43:22.701 --> 43:24.401
I got documents saying
I'm their legal guardian

43:24.402 --> 43:25.736
just like if I was their daddy.

43:25.738 --> 43:26.871
Now where's that money you owe?

43:26.872 --> 43:28.739
Their time and my meal.

44:32.235 --> 44:34.603
- You fuckin' parasite.
- Who the hell are you?

44:37.074 --> 44:39.074
- Stay down, stay down, stay down.
- Shh, shh, shh.

44:39.142 --> 44:42.078
- Stay down.
- Everything's fine. You're safe.

44:42.079 --> 44:43.779
Come with me.

44:43.780 --> 44:45.347
Quiet.

44:45.348 --> 44:46.982
All right.

44:50.285 --> 44:52.086
Sorry about that.

44:54.256 --> 44:57.625
So tomorrow I'll be by to
talk to you about some things.

44:57.626 --> 44:59.527
Medical things.

44:59.528 --> 45:02.030
But for now, I want you to rest up.

45:02.031 --> 45:04.465
You're safe here.

45:04.533 --> 45:07.835
Mr. Cleary will be with
you as long as you want.

45:07.937 --> 45:10.938
And he'll be just outside
the door while you sleep.

45:12.808 --> 45:14.808
I'll see you in the morning.

45:17.813 --> 45:19.447
Don't worry.

45:19.514 --> 45:21.649
I ain't gonna let nothing
happen to you girls.

45:21.650 --> 45:23.851
- Do you mind?
- No.

45:25.153 --> 45:27.354
So, uh...

45:27.356 --> 45:28.923
don't peg me as rude or nothing,

45:29.124 --> 45:31.492
but you two got me asking all
kinds of questions in my head.

45:31.493 --> 45:34.461
Like for instance,

45:34.463 --> 45:36.597
how do you two take a shite?

45:36.698 --> 45:39.166
Is it together like or does it
all just go through one of you?

45:43.238 --> 45:45.472
Now, I'm going to place a clamp

45:45.474 --> 45:47.808
on the hepatoduodenal ligament.

46:06.161 --> 46:08.661
Normally, when you cut into the liver,

46:08.696 --> 46:12.332
the hemorrhaging would
be enormous, but watch.

46:21.375 --> 46:22.876
There's virtually no blood loss.

46:22.877 --> 46:24.844
And our patient?

46:29.183 --> 46:31.217
Pulse is steady.

46:31.218 --> 46:34.453
This is the key to the separation.

46:34.521 --> 46:36.855
We enter here at the
bottom where they're joined,

46:36.890 --> 46:40.326
get access to the
ligament and clamp it off.

46:40.393 --> 46:43.529
The delicate work will be
to split the liver in half,

46:43.530 --> 46:45.797
giving equal amount to each girl

46:45.866 --> 46:48.934
so that it can regenerate
evenly in both of them.

46:49.069 --> 46:51.036
We should also be
concerned about not damaging

46:51.070 --> 46:53.204
the peritoneum around the intestines.

46:53.306 --> 46:56.308
I'm more concerned about that
Brockhurst fellow showing up again.

46:56.309 --> 46:58.676
Oh, I've taken care of that.

47:02.614 --> 47:04.715
Harry.

47:04.817 --> 47:08.419
You two waiting for the rest
of your ball team to show up?

47:08.454 --> 47:10.488
Just looking out for a scum sucker.

47:10.489 --> 47:12.323
What brings you around here?

47:12.424 --> 47:15.660
I was going to see if I could
get a bed for a girl in trouble.

47:15.661 --> 47:17.829
Not so sure if I should go in, though.

47:17.830 --> 47:18.996
You want I should ask for you?

47:18.997 --> 47:20.798
Appreciate it.

47:20.899 --> 47:24.234
Though you might want to
leave my name out of it.

47:24.236 --> 47:26.103
You're looking a bit pale.

47:26.104 --> 47:27.839
Are you sick?

47:27.840 --> 47:29.707
Not eating much.

47:30.743 --> 47:32.409
Let's buy you some lunch.

47:32.478 --> 47:34.811
Pounce can watch the
door by himself for a bit.

47:34.846 --> 47:36.780
If you bring me back a sausage.

47:36.781 --> 47:38.915
If you got some money.

47:44.321 --> 47:45.922
Thanks.

47:55.832 --> 47:58.568
You ain't gonna find a better
beef and Guinness pie around.

47:58.668 --> 48:01.804
Close your eyes and you'll
think you're in Dublin.

48:03.440 --> 48:05.174
What's the matter?

48:05.175 --> 48:07.643
Nothing.

48:07.644 --> 48:10.145
I paid 10 cents for that.

48:10.147 --> 48:12.381
You've got to eat something.

48:12.383 --> 48:14.817
Get that color back in your cheeks.

48:20.991 --> 48:22.691
What is it?

48:22.692 --> 48:25.461
I'm fine. Just go about your food.

48:25.462 --> 48:27.063
Oh, Christ, Harry.

48:27.064 --> 48:29.031
I don't want your pity.

48:29.066 --> 48:31.400
Then I won't give it to
you, but for fuck's sake,

48:31.501 --> 48:34.237
it's all right to let me of
all people see you hurting.

48:34.238 --> 48:35.938
Why you?

48:35.972 --> 48:38.373
What makes you think you're so special?

48:38.542 --> 48:42.477
I'm the only one who never thought
you was rock-hard from the start.

48:42.512 --> 48:44.412
I knew you were soft under that habit.

48:44.414 --> 48:47.550
Human. Or you gonna deny that, too?

48:47.551 --> 48:49.552
I never said I wasn't human.

48:49.553 --> 48:52.019
Yeah, well, no human deserves

48:52.154 --> 48:54.688
to take the beating you've been
taking these last few months.

48:54.690 --> 48:56.758
I think all the time, you know,

48:56.826 --> 49:00.327
if it's killing me, what's it doing to her?

49:00.329 --> 49:02.864
It's breaking me, that's what.

49:04.399 --> 49:06.734
I've got less than nothing.

49:06.735 --> 49:09.537
I'm useless. No good to anyone.

49:09.538 --> 49:11.906
No job, no calling.

49:11.907 --> 49:13.908
No purpose.

49:15.110 --> 49:17.712
It ain't easy

49:17.713 --> 49:20.448
losing what you lost.

49:20.449 --> 49:22.517
Defrocked.

49:22.518 --> 49:25.186
Unmasked.

49:25.220 --> 49:29.257
I got nowhere to turn, no one who cares.

49:29.291 --> 49:31.859
I can't even stand up
to the sisters anymore.

49:31.894 --> 49:34.461
I'm scared as all the rest of them.

49:34.529 --> 49:37.430
With no job, they're going to kick me out.

49:37.431 --> 49:40.033
I'm bound for the street.

49:40.034 --> 49:41.868
Those fucking goats.

49:41.903 --> 49:44.337
It's a charity home. They can't do that.

49:44.472 --> 49:47.573
They can if they're charging me
for a bed and I got no way to pay.

49:47.642 --> 49:50.076
What about the $3 I've
been sending you every week?

49:52.146 --> 49:54.380
What $3?

49:56.484 --> 49:58.619
You ain't been getting it?

49:58.620 --> 50:00.720
Those holy fucking sisters.

50:00.822 --> 50:03.089
They've been flogging you day
and night for what you done

50:03.090 --> 50:04.391
and then they steal your money.

50:04.392 --> 50:06.660
Bunch of wicked cunts!

50:06.661 --> 50:08.862
It makes no difference.

50:08.930 --> 50:11.698
Your handouts or theirs,
I'm still a charity case.

50:11.733 --> 50:13.099
I don't know what I'm going to do.

50:13.100 --> 50:14.734
This is what you're going to do.

50:14.735 --> 50:16.502
You're going to leave that place

50:16.504 --> 50:18.103
and you're going to live with me.

50:18.105 --> 50:19.505
That ain't a fucking invitation.

50:19.606 --> 50:21.641
I told you I had the lady
down the hall make a curtain.

50:21.642 --> 50:23.409
So you make up whatever rules you like

50:23.411 --> 50:25.478
and I'll follow them to the tee.

50:25.479 --> 50:26.779
But you're coming with me.

50:26.780 --> 50:29.114
And that's that.

50:31.252 --> 50:32.752
Think I could get a whiskey?

50:32.753 --> 50:34.754
Have mine.

50:35.689 --> 50:37.990
Wicked fucking cunts.

51:10.056 --> 51:12.391
Would you like me to heat up
last night's roast for you?

51:12.392 --> 51:14.458
No.

51:18.731 --> 51:20.698
Thank you

51:20.733 --> 51:23.334
for taking care of so
much these past few days.

51:26.371 --> 51:28.306
I'm happy to help.

51:34.179 --> 51:36.147
You brighten my spirits.

51:40.019 --> 51:42.887
Well, I think I may be able
to brighten them a bit more.

51:44.923 --> 51:47.090
You don't know it yet,

51:47.158 --> 51:51.061
but Saturday is going
to be a red-letter day

51:51.096 --> 51:55.432
in the life of Dr. Bertram Chickering Jr.

51:55.433 --> 51:57.334
- Oh?
- Mmm.

52:03.775 --> 52:06.743
Is it some kind of holiday?

52:06.745 --> 52:09.546
Yeah, you could call it that.

52:09.580 --> 52:14.117
Uh, Cecily is visiting
her brother at Harvard

52:14.118 --> 52:16.485
and won't be back until Sunday,

52:16.586 --> 52:21.190
so that means we have my
apartment all to ourselves.

52:32.435 --> 52:34.870
Is that for the ball?

52:36.106 --> 52:38.274
Yes.

52:40.610 --> 52:42.244
Once this procedure is done,

52:42.279 --> 52:44.780
no one will stare at them like freaks,

52:44.781 --> 52:47.248
like they're monsters.

52:47.383 --> 52:50.418
Can you imagine how they'll
feel when they're finally normal?

52:51.754 --> 52:53.588
No...

52:53.589 --> 52:55.791
I can't.

52:55.792 --> 52:58.426
Oh, that's not what I meant.

52:58.494 --> 53:01.062
- I'm sorry. I just get excited.
- Stop it, John.

53:02.231 --> 53:04.399
I am what I am and I can live with that.

53:05.802 --> 53:07.769
But I can't live like this.

53:07.770 --> 53:09.404
I don't understand.

53:09.405 --> 53:11.806
I can't live with you here, John.

53:14.943 --> 53:17.311
You arrived one night and you were back.

53:19.447 --> 53:22.383
You needed me and I... I wanted that.

53:24.252 --> 53:27.621
So I wait for your knock on my door.

53:27.655 --> 53:31.792
No matter what the hour, I wait here,

53:31.793 --> 53:33.660
hoping you'll come.

53:35.463 --> 53:38.532
Even though I know you've just
been with some other woman.

53:38.533 --> 53:40.100
Abby.

53:40.168 --> 53:42.469
And you have every right.
I have no claim on you.

53:45.173 --> 53:48.274
What could a woman like me
rightly expect from any man?

53:51.379 --> 53:53.346
But it's too hard now...

53:55.316 --> 53:57.517
knowing we'll never be together.

53:59.987 --> 54:01.888
I can't fool myself any longer

54:01.889 --> 54:04.223
and it's...

54:04.225 --> 54:06.292
Being near you is just too painful.

54:07.895 --> 54:09.730
Abby, I love you.

54:09.731 --> 54:11.965
- Oh.
- I never stopped.

54:11.966 --> 54:13.399
You only come here to talk.

54:13.401 --> 54:16.503
You go elsewhere for everything else.

54:16.504 --> 54:18.538
Please just leave.

54:18.539 --> 54:20.640
Abby.

54:20.641 --> 54:23.175
I need you to go.

54:26.480 --> 54:28.280
No.

